title: Best 80's Movies + Isolated Guitar Track Game + Josh Turner In Studio
itunes:title: Best 80's Movies + Isolated Guitar Track Game + Josh Turner In Studio
description:
Amy watched 'Back To The Future' with her kids recently and they loved it...so Bobby and Amy share some of their favorite 80's movies! Bobby plays only the isolated guitar track from famous country songs and the show members have to try and guess the songs. Plus, Josh Turner stops by the studio to chat and perform!
